      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca-0)))
              (cat c-0 (pubk c-0)
                (enc (hash c-0 (pubk c-0)) (privk ca-0)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca-0)))
                  (cat c-0 (pubk c-0)
                    (enc (hash c-0 (pubk c-0)) (privk ca-0)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c-0))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s)
                      (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca-0)))
                    (cat c-0 (pubk c-0)
                      (enc (hash c-0 (pubk c-0)) (privk ca-0)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))

                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)

                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c-0))))

        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))

      (send (cat sr-1 s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca-0))))
      (recv
        (cat
          (cat c-0 (pubk c-0) (enc (hash c-0 (pubk c-0)) (privk ca-0)))
          (enc pms-1 (pubk s))

            (hash cr-1 sr-1
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca-0)))

                    (enc pms-1 (pubk s))) (privk c-0))))

      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms-1 "server finished"
            (hash cr-1 sr-1
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca-0)))

                (enc (hash c-0 (pubk c-0)) (privk ca-0)))

                    (enc (hash c-0 (pubk c-0)) (privk ca-0)))
                  (enc pms-1 (pubk s))) (privk c-0))

                (hash pms-1 "client finished"
                  (hash cr-1 sr-1
                    (cat s (pubk s)
                      (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca-0)))

(defprotocol ca basic
  (defrole clienta
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (p password)
      (cookie any mesg) (cookiestor locn) (request httpreq)
      (response httpdata))
    (trace (send cr)
      (recv (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (recv
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (send (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv
        (enc "login-successful" cookie
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))) (load cookiestor any)
      (stor cookiestor (cat "client store" u s cookie))
      (send (enc cookie request (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))))
  (defrole clientr
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (cookie mesg)
      (cookiestor locn) (request httpreq) (response httpdata))
    (trace (send cr)
      (recv (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))

            (hash cr sr

              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))

            (hash pms "client finished"

                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))

                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (recv
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"

                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))

                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (load cookiestor (cat "client store" u s cookie))
      (send (enc cookie request (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    (gen-st (cat "client store" u s cookie)))
  (defrole servera
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (p password)
      (cookie data) (ppk skey) (any mesg) (authstor locn)
      (request httpreq) (response httpdata))
    (trace (recv cr)
      (send (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (recv
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))

                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send
        (enc "login-successful" (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr)))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))) (load authstor any)
      (stor authstor (cat "server store" s u cookie))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    (non-orig ppk)
    (uniq-orig cookie)
    (facts (neq u s)))
  (defrole serverr
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (cookie data)
      (ppk skey) (authstor locn) (request httpreq) (response httpdata))
    (trace (recv cr)
      (send (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (recv
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))

            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (load authstor (cat "server store" s u cookie))
      (send (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    (non-orig ppk)
    (facts (neq u s))
    (gen-st (cat "server store" s u cookie)))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct1
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clienta" "c" z c) (p "clienta" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct2
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clienta" "c" z c) (p "clientr" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct3
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" "c" z c) (p "clientr" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct4
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" "c" z c) (p "clienta" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_indx
    (forall ((x indx)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_strd
    (forall ((x strd)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_mesg
    (forall ((x mesg)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule scissorsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (trans z2 i2)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1) (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (and (= z1 z2) (= i1 i2)))))
  (defgenrule cakeRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2)) (false))))
  (defgenrule no-interruption
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2) (trans z1 i1)
          (same-locn z0 i0 z1 i1) (prec z0 i0 z1 i1) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2))
        (false))))
  (defgenrule shearsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (trans z2 i2)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1) (same-locn z0 i0 z2 i2)
          (prec z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (or (and (= z1 z2) (= i1 i2)) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2)))))
  (defgenrule invShearsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (same-locn z0 i0 z1 i1)
          (leads-to z1 i1 z2 i2) (prec z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (or (and (= z0 z1) (= i0 i1)) (prec z0 i0 z1 i1)))))
  (defgenrule fact-servera-neq0
    (forall ((z strd) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "servera" z (idx 5)) (p "servera" "s" z s)
          (p "servera" "u" z u)) (fact neq u s))))
  (defgenrule fact-serverr-neq0
    (forall ((z strd) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "serverr" z (idx 6)) (p "serverr" "s" z s)
          (p "serverr" "u" z u)) (fact neq u s))))
  (defgenrule trRl_clienta-at-7
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "clienta" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 7)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_clienta-at-6
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "clienta" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 6)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_servera-at-7
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "servera" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 7)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_servera-at-6
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "servera" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 6)))))
  (defgenrule gen-st-clientr-0
    (forall ((z strd) (cookie mesg) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" z (idx 5)) (p "clientr" "cookie" z cookie)
          (p "clientr" "s" z s) (p "clientr" "u" z u))
        (gen-st (cat "client store" u s cookie)))))
  (defgenrule gen-st-serverr-0
    (forall ((z strd) (cookie data) (u s name))
      (implies
        (and (p "serverr" z (idx 6)) (p "serverr" "cookie" z cookie)
          (p "serverr" "u" z u) (p "serverr" "s" z s))
        (gen-st (cat "server store" s u cookie)))))
  (lang (random32 atom) (random48 atom) (password atom) (httpreq atom)
    (httpdata atom)))

(defskeleton ca
  (vars (any mesg) (cookie data) (request httpreq) (p password)
    (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (ppk skey) (c s ca u name)
    (pt pt-0 pval) (authstor locn))
  (defstrand servera 9 (any any) (cookie cookie) (request request) (p p)
    (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (ppk ppk) (c c) (u u) (s s) (ca ca)
    (authstor authstor))
  (non-orig ppk (privk c) (privk s) (privk ca))
  (uniq-orig cookie sr)
  (traces
    ((recv cr)
      (send (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (recv
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (send

          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))

                (hash cr sr

                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send
        (enc "login-successful" (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr)))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (load authstor (cat pt any))
      (stor authstor (cat pt-0 "server store" s u cookie))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
    ((send cr)
      (recv (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))))
    ((recv cr-0)
      (send (cat sr-0 s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))))

(defskeleton ca
  (vars (any mesg) (cookie data) (request httpreq) (p password)
    (cr sr cr-0 sr-0 cr-1 sr-1 random32) (pms pms-0 random48) (ppk skey)

(defprotocol ca basic
  (defrole clienta
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (p password)
      (cookie any mesg) (cookiestor locn) (request httpreq)
      (response httpdata))
    (trace (send cr)
      (recv (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))

            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))

            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (recv
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))

                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))

                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))

          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))

        (enc "login-successful" cookie
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))) (load cookiestor any)
      (stor cookiestor (cat "client store" u s cookie))
      (send (enc cookie request (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))))

                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (load authstor (cat "server store" s u cookie))
      (send (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    (non-orig ppk)
    (facts (neq u s))
    (gen-st (cat "server store" s u cookie)))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct1
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clienta" "c" z c) (p "clienta" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct2
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clienta" "c" z c) (p "clientr" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct3
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" "c" z c) (p "clientr" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct4
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" "c" z c) (p "clienta" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_indx
    (forall ((x indx)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_strd
    (forall ((x strd)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_mesg
    (forall ((x mesg)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule scissorsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (trans z2 i2)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1) (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (and (= z1 z2) (= i1 i2)))))
  (defgenrule cakeRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2)) (false))))
  (defgenrule no-interruption
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2) (trans z1 i1)
          (same-locn z0 i0 z1 i1) (prec z0 i0 z1 i1) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2))
        (false))))
  (defgenrule shearsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (trans z2 i2)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1) (same-locn z0 i0 z2 i2)
          (prec z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (or (and (= z1 z2) (= i1 i2)) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2)))))
  (defgenrule invShearsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (same-locn z0 i0 z1 i1)
          (leads-to z1 i1 z2 i2) (prec z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (or (and (= z0 z1) (= i0 i1)) (prec z0 i0 z1 i1)))))
  (defgenrule fact-servera-neq0
    (forall ((z strd) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "servera" z (idx 5)) (p "servera" "s" z s)
          (p "servera" "u" z u)) (fact neq u s))))
  (defgenrule fact-serverr-neq0
    (forall ((z strd) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "serverr" z (idx 6)) (p "serverr" "s" z s)
          (p "serverr" "u" z u)) (fact neq u s))))
  (defgenrule trRl_clienta-at-7
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "clienta" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 7)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_clienta-at-6
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "clienta" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 6)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_servera-at-7
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "servera" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 7)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_servera-at-6
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "servera" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 6)))))
  (defgenrule gen-st-clientr-0
    (forall ((z strd) (cookie mesg) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" z (idx 5)) (p "clientr" "cookie" z cookie)
          (p "clientr" "s" z s) (p "clientr" "u" z u))
        (gen-st (cat "client store" u s cookie)))))
  (defgenrule gen-st-serverr-0
    (forall ((z strd) (cookie data) (u s name))
      (implies
        (and (p "serverr" z (idx 6)) (p "serverr" "cookie" z cookie)
          (p "serverr" "u" z u) (p "serverr" "s" z s))
        (gen-st (cat "server store" s u cookie)))))
  (lang (random32 atom) (random48 atom) (password atom) (httpreq atom)
    (httpdata atom)))

(defskeleton ca
  (vars (any mesg) (cookie data) (request httpreq) (p password)
    (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (ppk skey) (c s ca u name)
    (pt pt-0 pval) (authstor locn))
  (defstrand servera 9 (any any) (cookie cookie) (request request) (p p)
    (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (ppk ppk) (c c) (u u) (s s) (ca ca)
    (authstor authstor))
  (non-orig ppk (privk c) (privk s) (privk ca))
  (uniq-orig cookie cr sr pms)
  (traces
    ((recv cr)
      (send (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (recv
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send
        (enc "login-successful" (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr)))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (load authstor (cat pt any))
      (stor authstor (cat pt-0 "server store" s u cookie))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))))
  (label 138)
  (unrealized (0 2))
  (origs (pt-0 (0 7)) (sr (0 1)) (cookie (0 5)))
  (comment "Not closed under rules"))

  (vars (any mesg) (cookie data) (request httpreq) (p password)
    (cr sr cr-0 sr-0 random32) (pms random48) (ppk skey) (c ca u s name)

    (cr sr cr-0 sr-0 cr-1 sr-1 random32) (pms pms-0 random48) (ppk skey)
    (c s ca u s-0 name) (pt pt-0 pval) (authstor locn))
  (defstrand servera 9 (any any) (cookie cookie) (request request) (p p)
    (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (ppk ppk) (c c) (u u) (s s) (ca ca)
    (authstor authstor))
  (defstrand clientr 3 (cr cr-0) (sr sr-0) (pms pms-0) (c c) (s s-0)
    (ca ca))
  (defstrand serverr 2 (cr cr-1) (sr sr-1) (s s-0) (ca ca))
  (defstrand clientr 3 (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (c c) (s s) (ca ca))
  (deflistener (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))
  (precedes ((0 1) (3 1)) ((1 2) (0 2)) ((2 1) (1 1)) ((3 0) (0 0))
    ((3 2) (0 2)) ((4 1) (0 4)))
  (non-orig ppk (privk c) (privk s) (privk ca))
  (uniq-orig cookie cr sr pms)
  (facts (neq u s))
  (rule fact-servera-neq0 trRl_servera-at-6 trRl_servera-at-7)
  (operation encryption-test
    (added-listener (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))
    (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")) (0 4))
  (traces
    ((recv cr)
      (send (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (recv
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send
        (enc "login-successful" (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr)))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (load authstor (cat pt any))
      (stor authstor (cat pt-0 "server store" s u cookie))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
    ((send cr-0)
      (recv
        (cat sr-0 s-0 (pubk s-0)
          (enc (hash s-0 (pubk s-0)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms-0 (pubk s-0))
          (enc
            (hash cr-0 sr-0
              (cat s-0 (pubk s-0)
                (enc (hash s-0 (pubk s-0)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms-0 (pubk s-0))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms-0 "client finished"
              (hash cr-0 sr-0
                (cat s-0 (pubk s-0)
                  (enc (hash s-0 (pubk s-0)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms-0 (pubk s-0))
                (enc
                  (hash cr-0 sr-0
                    (cat s-0 (pubk s-0)
                      (enc (hash s-0 (pubk s-0)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms-0 (pubk s-0))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms-0 cr-0 sr-0) "client_write")))))
    ((recv cr-1)
      (send
        (cat sr-1 s-0 (pubk s-0)
          (enc (hash s-0 (pubk s-0)) (privk ca)))))
    ((send cr)
      (recv (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))))
    ((recv (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))
      (send (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
  (label 159)
  (parent 149)
  (unrealized (0 8) (4 0))
  (comment "1 in cohort - 1 not yet seen"))

(defskeleton ca

    (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (ppk ppk) (c c) (u u) (s s) (ca ca)

  (defstrand clienta 5 (p p) (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (c c) (u u) (s s)
    (ca ca))
  (precedes ((0 1) (2 1)) ((0 3) (2 3)) ((1 1) (0 2)) ((2 0) (0 0))
    ((2 2) (0 2)) ((2 4) (0 4)))
  (non-orig ppk (privk c) (privk s) (privk ca))

  (facts (neq u s))
  (rule fact-servera-neq0 trRl_servera-at-6 trRl_servera-at-7)
  (operation encryption-test (displaced 3 0 serverr 4)
    (enc
      (hash pms "server finished"
        (hash cr sr (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
          (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))

            (hash cr sr

              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))

            (hash pms "client finished"

                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))

                  (hash cr sr

                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")) (2 3))

    (cr sr cr-0 sr-0 random32) (pms pms-0 random48) (ppk skey)
    (c s ca u name) (pt pt-0 pval) (authstor locn))
  (defstrand servera 9 (any any) (cookie cookie) (request request) (p p)
    (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (ppk ppk) (c c) (u u) (s s) (ca ca)
    (authstor authstor))
  (defstrand clientr 3 (cr cr-0) (sr sr-0) (pms pms-0) (c c) (s s)
    (ca ca))
  (defstrand clientr 3 (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (c c) (s s) (ca ca))
  (deflistener (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))
  (deflistener (cat (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))
  (deflistener (cat pms cr sr))
  (precedes ((0 1) (1 1)) ((0 1) (2 1)) ((1 2) (0 2)) ((2 0) (0 0))
    ((2 2) (0 2)) ((2 2) (5 0)) ((3 1) (0 4)) ((4 1) (3 0))
    ((5 1) (4 0)))
  (non-orig ppk (privk c) (privk s) (privk ca))
  (uniq-orig cookie cr sr pms)
  (facts (neq u s))
  (rule fact-servera-neq0 trRl_servera-at-6 trRl_servera-at-7)
  (operation encryption-test (added-listener (cat pms cr sr))
    (hash pms cr sr) (4 0))
  (traces
    ((recv cr)
      (send (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (recv
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send
        (enc "login-successful" (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr)))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (load authstor (cat pt any))
      (stor authstor (cat pt-0 "server store" s u cookie))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
    ((send cr-0)
      (recv (cat sr-0 s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms-0 (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr-0 sr-0
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms-0 (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms-0 "client finished"
              (hash cr-0 sr-0
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms-0 (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr-0 sr-0
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms-0 (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms-0 cr-0 sr-0) "client_write")))))
    ((send cr)
      (recv (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))))
    ((recv (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))
      (send (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
    ((recv (cat (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))
      (send (cat (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
    ((recv (cat pms cr sr)) (send (cat pms cr sr))))
  (label 186)
  (parent 168)
  (unrealized (5 0))
  (dead)
  (comment "empty cohort"))

(defskeleton ca
  (vars (any any-0 mesg) (cookie data) (request httpreq) (p password)
    (cr sr cr-0 sr-0 random32) (pms random48) (ppk skey) (c u s ca name)
    (pt pt-0 pt-1 pt-2 pval) (authstor cookiestor locn))
  (defstrand servera 9 (any any) (cookie cookie) (request request) (p p)
    (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (ppk ppk) (c c) (u u) (s s) (ca ca)
    (authstor authstor))
  (defstrand serverr 2 (cr cr-0) (sr sr-0) (s s) (ca ca))
  (defstrand clienta 9 (cookie (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))))
    (any any-0) (request request) (p p) (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (c c)
    (u u) (s s) (ca ca) (cookiestor cookiestor))
  (precedes ((0 1) (2 1)) ((0 3) (2 3)) ((0 5) (2 5)) ((1 1) (2 1))
    ((2 0) (0 0)) ((2 2) (0 2)) ((2 4) (0 4)) ((2 8) (0 8)))
  (non-orig ppk (privk c) (privk s) (privk ca))
  (uniq-orig cookie cr sr pms)
  (facts (neq u s))
  (rule fact-servera-neq0 trRl_clienta-at-6 trRl_clienta-at-7
    trRl_servera-at-6 trRl_servera-at-7)
  (operation encryption-test (displaced 2 3 clienta 9)
    (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
      (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")) (0 8))
  (traces

            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))

                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))

      (send (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
    ((recv (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))
      (send (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))

(defskeleton ca
  (vars (any mesg) (cookie data) (request httpreq) (p password)
    (cr sr cr-0 sr-0 random32) (pms pms-0 random48) (ppk skey)

    (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (ppk ppk) (c c) (u u) (s s) (ca ca)

    (ca ca))

        (cat sr s-0 (pubk s-0) (enc (hash s-0 (pubk s-0)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s-0))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s-0 (pubk s-0)
                (enc (hash s-0 (pubk s-0)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s-0))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s-0 (pubk s-0)
                  (enc (hash s-0 (pubk s-0)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s-0))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s-0 (pubk s-0)

                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s-0))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (recv
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s-0 (pubk s-0)
                (enc (hash s-0 (pubk s-0)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s-0))

                    (cat s-0 (pubk s-0)
                      (enc (hash s-0 (pubk s-0)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s-0))

                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s-0 (pubk s-0)

                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s-0))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (send (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
    ((recv (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))
      (send (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))

(defskeleton ca
  (vars (any mesg) (cookie data) (request httpreq) (p password)
    (cr sr cr-0 sr-0 random32) (pms random48) (ppk skey) (u c s ca name)
    (pt pt-0 pval) (authstor locn))
  (defstrand servera 9 (any any) (cookie cookie) (request request) (p p)
    (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (ppk ppk) (c c) (u u) (s s) (ca ca)
    (authstor authstor))
  (defstrand serverr 2 (cr cr-0) (sr sr-0) (s c) (ca ca))
  (defstrand clienta 5 (p p) (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (c c) (u u) (s s)
    (ca ca))
  (deflistener (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))
  (deflistener (cat (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))
  (deflistener (cat pms cr sr))
  (precedes ((0 1) (2 1)) ((0 3) (2 3)) ((1 1) (0 2)) ((2 0) (0 0))
    ((2 2) (0 2)) ((2 2) (5 0)) ((2 4) (0 4)) ((3 1) (0 8))
    ((4 1) (3 0)) ((5 1) (4 0)))
  (non-orig ppk (privk c) (privk s) (privk ca))
  (uniq-orig cookie cr sr pms)
  (facts (neq u s))
  (rule fact-servera-neq0 trRl_servera-at-6 trRl_servera-at-7)
  (operation encryption-test (added-listener (cat pms cr sr))
    (hash pms cr sr) (4 0))
  (traces
    ((recv cr)
      (send (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (recv
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send
        (enc "login-successful" (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr)))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (load authstor (cat pt any))
      (stor authstor (cat pt-0 "server store" s u cookie))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
    ((recv cr-0)
      (send (cat sr-0 c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))))

(defprotocol ca basic
  (defrole clienta
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (p password)
      (cookie any mesg) (cookiestor locn) (request httpreq)
      (response httpdata))
    (trace (send cr)
      (recv (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (recv
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (send (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv
        (enc "login-successful" cookie
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))) (load cookiestor any)
      (stor cookiestor (cat "client store" u s cookie))
      (send (enc cookie request (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))))

        (enc "login-successful" (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr)))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))) (load authstor any)
      (stor authstor (cat "server store" s u cookie))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    (non-orig ppk)
    (uniq-orig cookie)
    (facts (neq u s)))
  (defrole serverr
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (cookie data)
      (ppk skey) (authstor locn) (request httpreq) (response httpdata))
    (trace (recv cr)
      (send (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (recv
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (load authstor (cat "server store" s u cookie))
      (send (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    (non-orig ppk)
    (facts (neq u s))
    (gen-st (cat "server store" s u cookie)))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct1
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clienta" "c" z c) (p "clienta" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct2
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clienta" "c" z c) (p "clientr" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct3
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" "c" z c) (p "clientr" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct4
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" "c" z c) (p "clienta" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_indx
    (forall ((x indx)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_strd
    (forall ((x strd)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_mesg
    (forall ((x mesg)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule scissorsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (trans z2 i2)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1) (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (and (= z1 z2) (= i1 i2)))))
  (defgenrule cakeRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2)) (false))))
  (defgenrule no-interruption
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2) (trans z1 i1)
          (same-locn z0 i0 z1 i1) (prec z0 i0 z1 i1) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2))
        (false))))
  (defgenrule shearsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (trans z2 i2)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1) (same-locn z0 i0 z2 i2)
          (prec z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (or (and (= z1 z2) (= i1 i2)) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2)))))
  (defgenrule invShearsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (same-locn z0 i0 z1 i1)
          (leads-to z1 i1 z2 i2) (prec z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (or (and (= z0 z1) (= i0 i1)) (prec z0 i0 z1 i1)))))
  (defgenrule fact-servera-neq0
    (forall ((z strd) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "servera" z (idx 5)) (p "servera" "s" z s)
          (p "servera" "u" z u)) (fact neq u s))))
  (defgenrule fact-serverr-neq0
    (forall ((z strd) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "serverr" z (idx 6)) (p "serverr" "s" z s)
          (p "serverr" "u" z u)) (fact neq u s))))
  (defgenrule trRl_clienta-at-7
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "clienta" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 7)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_clienta-at-6
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "clienta" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 6)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_servera-at-7
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "servera" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 7)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_servera-at-6
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "servera" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 6)))))
  (defgenrule gen-st-clientr-0
    (forall ((z strd) (cookie mesg) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" z (idx 5)) (p "clientr" "cookie" z cookie)
          (p "clientr" "s" z s) (p "clientr" "u" z u))
        (gen-st (cat "client store" u s cookie)))))
  (defgenrule gen-st-serverr-0
    (forall ((z strd) (cookie data) (u s name))
      (implies
        (and (p "serverr" z (idx 6)) (p "serverr" "cookie" z cookie)
          (p "serverr" "u" z u) (p "serverr" "s" z s))
        (gen-st (cat "server store" s u cookie)))))
  (lang (random32 atom) (random48 atom) (password atom) (httpreq atom)
    (httpdata atom)))

(defskeleton ca
  (vars (cookie data) (request httpreq) (cr sr cr-0 sr-0 random32)
    (pms random48) (ppk skey) (c ca u s name) (pt pval) (authstor locn))

    (pms pms) (ppk ppk) (c c) (u u) (s s) (ca ca) (authstor authstor))
  (defstrand clientr 3 (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (c c) (s s) (ca ca))
  (defstrand serverr 2 (cr cr-0) (sr sr-0) (s s) (ca ca))
  (deflistener (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr)))
  (precedes ((0 1) (1 1)) ((1 2) (0 2)) ((2 1) (1 1)) ((3 1) (0 4)))
  (non-orig ppk (privk c) (privk ca) (privk s))
  (uniq-orig sr)
  (gen-st (cat "server store" s u cookie))
  (facts (neq u s))
  (rule fact-serverr-neq0)

    (ca ca))
  (defstrand serverr 2 (cr cr-1) (sr sr-1) (s s-0) (ca ca))
  (defstrand clientr 3 (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (c c) (s s) (ca ca))

(defprotocol ca basic
  (defrole clienta
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (p password)
      (cookie any mesg) (cookiestor locn) (request httpreq)
      (response httpdata))
    (trace (send cr)
      (recv (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (recv
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (send (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv
        (enc "login-successful" cookie
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))) (load cookiestor any)
      (stor cookiestor (cat "client store" u s cookie))
      (send (enc cookie request (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))))
  (defrole clientr
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (cookie mesg)
      (cookiestor locn) (request httpreq) (response httpdata))
    (trace (send cr)
      (recv (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (recv
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (load cookiestor (cat "client store" u s cookie))
      (send (enc cookie request (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    (gen-st (cat "client store" u s cookie)))
  (defrole servera
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (p password)

      (recv (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send
        (enc "login-successful" (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr)))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))) (load authstor any)
      (stor authstor (cat "server store" s u cookie))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    (non-orig ppk)
    (uniq-orig cookie)
    (facts (neq u s)))
  (defrole serverr
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (cookie data)
      (ppk skey) (authstor locn) (request httpreq) (response httpdata))
    (trace (recv cr)
      (send (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (recv
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (load authstor (cat "server store" s u cookie))
      (send (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    (non-orig ppk)
    (facts (neq u s))
    (gen-st (cat "server store" s u cookie)))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct1
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clienta" "c" z c) (p "clienta" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct2
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clienta" "c" z c) (p "clientr" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct3
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" "c" z c) (p "clientr" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defrule clients-servers-distinct4
    (forall ((z z-0 strd) (c name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" "c" z c) (p "clienta" "s" z-0 c))
        (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_indx
    (forall ((x indx)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_strd
    (forall ((x strd)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule neqRl_mesg
    (forall ((x mesg)) (implies (fact neq x x) (false))))
  (defgenrule scissorsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (trans z2 i2)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1) (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (and (= z1 z2) (= i1 i2)))))
  (defgenrule cakeRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2)) (false))))
  (defgenrule no-interruption
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (leads-to z0 i0 z2 i2) (trans z1 i1)
          (same-locn z0 i0 z1 i1) (prec z0 i0 z1 i1) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2))
        (false))))
  (defgenrule shearsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (trans z2 i2)
          (leads-to z0 i0 z1 i1) (same-locn z0 i0 z2 i2)
          (prec z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (or (and (= z1 z2) (= i1 i2)) (prec z1 i1 z2 i2)))))
  (defgenrule invShearsRule
    (forall ((z0 z1 z2 strd) (i0 i1 i2 indx))
      (implies
        (and (trans z0 i0) (trans z1 i1) (same-locn z0 i0 z1 i1)
          (leads-to z1 i1 z2 i2) (prec z0 i0 z2 i2))
        (or (and (= z0 z1) (= i0 i1)) (prec z0 i0 z1 i1)))))
  (defgenrule fact-servera-neq0
    (forall ((z strd) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "servera" z (idx 5)) (p "servera" "s" z s)
          (p "servera" "u" z u)) (fact neq u s))))
  (defgenrule fact-serverr-neq0
    (forall ((z strd) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "serverr" z (idx 6)) (p "serverr" "s" z s)
          (p "serverr" "u" z u)) (fact neq u s))))
  (defgenrule trRl_clienta-at-7
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "clienta" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 7)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_clienta-at-6
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "clienta" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 6)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_servera-at-7
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "servera" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 7)))))
  (defgenrule trRl_servera-at-6
    (forall ((z strd))
      (implies (p "servera" z (idx 8)) (trans z (idx 6)))))
  (defgenrule gen-st-clientr-0
    (forall ((z strd) (cookie mesg) (s u name))
      (implies
        (and (p "clientr" z (idx 5)) (p "clientr" "cookie" z cookie)
          (p "clientr" "s" z s) (p "clientr" "u" z u))
        (gen-st (cat "client store" u s cookie)))))
  (defgenrule gen-st-serverr-0
    (forall ((z strd) (cookie data) (u s name))
      (implies
        (and (p "serverr" z (idx 6)) (p "serverr" "cookie" z cookie)
          (p "serverr" "u" z u) (p "serverr" "s" z s))
        (gen-st (cat "server store" s u cookie)))))
  (lang (random32 atom) (random48 atom) (password atom) (httpreq atom)
    (httpdata atom)))

(defskeleton ca
  (vars (any mesg) (cookie data) (response httpdata) (request httpreq)
    (p password) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (c u s ca name)
    (pt pt-0 pval) (cookiestor locn))
  (deflistener cookie)
  (defstrand clienta 10 (cookie cookie) (any any) (response response)
    (request request) (p p) (cr cr) (sr sr) (pms pms) (c c) (u u) (s s)
    (ca ca) (cookiestor cookiestor))
  (non-orig (privk c) (privk s) (privk ca))
  (pen-non-orig p)
  (uniq-orig cr sr pms)
  (goals
    (forall
      ((any mesg) (cookie data) (response httpdata) (request httpreq)
        (p password) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (c u s ca name)
        (cookiestor locn) (z z-0 strd))
      (implies
        (and (p "clienta" z 10) (p "" z-0 2) (p "clienta" "any" z any)
          (p "clienta" "cookie" z cookie)
          (p "clienta" "response" z response) (p "clienta" "c" z c)
          (p "clienta" "request" z request) (p "clienta" "p" z p)
          (p "clienta" "cr" z cr) (p "clienta" "sr" z sr)
          (p "clienta" "pms" z pms) (p "clienta" "u" z u)
          (p "clienta" "s" z s) (p "clienta" "ca" z ca)
          (p "clienta" "cookiestor" z cookiestor) (p "" "x" z-0 cookie)
          (non (privk c)) (non (privk s)) (non (privk ca)) (pnon p)
          (uniq sr) (uniq-at cr z 0) (uniq-at pms z 2)) (false))))
  (traces ((recv cookie) (send cookie))
    ((send cr)
      (recv (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (send
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
          (enc
            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))
                (enc
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (recv
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (send (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv
        (enc "login-successful" cookie
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (load cookiestor (cat pt any))
      (stor cookiestor (cat pt-0 "client store" u s cookie))
      (send (enc cookie request (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))))
  (label 228)
  (unrealized (1 1) (1 3) (1 5) (1 9))
  (origs (pt-0 (1 7)) (cr (1 0)) (pms (1 2)))
  (comment "Not closed under rules"))

                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (send (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv
        (enc "login-successful" cookie
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (load cookiestor (cat pt any))
      (stor cookiestor (cat pt-0 "client store" u s cookie))
      (send (enc cookie request (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (recv (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    ((recv cr-0)
      (send (cat sr-0 s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))))
    ((recv (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))
      (send (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
    ((recv (cat (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))
      (send (cat (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
    ((recv (cat pms cr sr)) (send (cat pms cr sr))))

  (defrole servera
    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (p password)
      (cookie data) (ppk skey) (any mesg) (authstor locn)
      (request httpreq) (response httpdata))
    (trace (recv cr)
      (send (cat sr s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca))))
      (recv
        (cat (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
          (enc pms (pubk s))
          (enc
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))

            (hash pms "client finished"
              (hash cr sr
                (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                (enc pms (pubk s))

                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
            (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
      (send
        (enc
          (hash pms "server finished"
            (hash cr sr
              (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
              (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
              (enc pms (pubk s))
              (enc
                (hash cr sr
                  (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                  (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                  (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))
              (enc
                (hash pms "client finished"
                  (hash cr sr
                    (cat s (pubk s) (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                    (cat c (pubk c) (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                    (enc pms (pubk s))
                    (enc
                      (hash cr sr
                        (cat s (pubk s)
                          (enc (hash s (pubk s)) (privk ca)))
                        (cat c (pubk c)
                          (enc (hash c (pubk c)) (privk ca)))
                        (enc pms (pubk s))) (privk c))))
                (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write"))))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write")))
      (recv (enc "login" u p (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send
        (enc "login-successful" (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr)))
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))) (load authstor any)
      (stor authstor (cat "server store" s u cookie))
      (recv
        (enc (enc cookie (hash ppk (hash pms cr sr))) request
          (hash (hash pms cr sr) "client_write")))
      (send (enc response (hash (hash pms cr sr) "server_write"))))
    (non-orig ppk)
    (uniq-orig cookie)
    (facts (neq u s)))

    (vars (c u s ca name) (cr sr random32) (pms random48) (cookie data)
      (ppk skey) (authstor locn) (request httpreq) (response httpdata))
    (trace (recv cr)

            (hash pms "client finished"
